column5: crossed the bridge last night and there is still lots of ice to the south , aproximatly from the last marina on the west side ( right if your looking south  ) across. pretty grey looking some rain and wind will help but temps sound like they may be a bit on the cool side for the next few days .  Lots of open water on the Couch side.  local private launche at the bridge may make a killing if things don't change .  but Terry said they would and he's neevveer wrong  TB
